{
  "stem": "8784.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Sometimes before, while we were still at Oskar Schindler's factory, we did receive a tattoo.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The tattoo was not a number, but it was a big KL.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a KL, K standing for [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Konzentrazionslager-- ?] L for Lager, K for [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Konzentrazions. ?] This was given to us yet in Schindler's camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Emalia, under the orders of, evidently, the-- Amon Geoth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was given to us to prevent us from escape.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- at that time, and feeling the-- a little safe under Schindler's mantle, a rumor had it that if you sucked out the tattoo right immediately after it was done, that could disappear, and then you would still have a chance to escape.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, actually, I was among that group of people that sucked out the tattoo.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know where-- why I wasn't full of fear in doing it, but I did do it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I sucked it out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And lo and behold, today I don't have a tattoo on my arm of KL.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And yet there are friends that were together with me and eventually were liberated together with me and survived the war, and they have a inch-and-a-half tattoo on their arm with the KL.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But when I got to Gross-Rosen, I no longer had a KL.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when we arrived in Gross-Rosen, we stayed all in a-- this group of 700, as I recall, stayed in one barrack.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were separated from the rest of the population of that concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were kept separate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had no knowledge on why we are being kept separate and what is to happen to us eventually.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
